  announcementId: dolos_day5_night_bedroom
  text: "Shift completed. You have done a great service today, Andromeda.\nAfter
    5 successful years of service, your efforts have been recognized. You have proved
    yourself a useful asset to the DOLOS Corporation.\nAnd for that, we can soon
    proceed with the \u201CErebus Initiative,\u201D where your data\u2014and mind\u2014shall
    be used to elevate humanity into a digital medium."
